# applcp

ApplCP REST Agent deployed on FACS


## Request Collection [/requests]

### List All Requests [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                 "requestId": [30397036, 30397040 ]
            }
        ]

## Custom Action on a request Option 1 [/requests/{request_id}/]
+ Parameters
    + request_id (number) - ID of the Request in the form of an integer

### Custom Action on a request Option 1 [POST]
You may execute a custom action using the following on the request. (Option 1) 

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "action": "execute",
            "requestExectionContext": {
                "requestId": 30397036,
                "requestHandle": "aValidRequestHandle"
            },
            "requestParameters": [
                {
                    "name": "key1",
                    "paramType": "BOOLEAN",
                    "value": "value1"
                },
                {
                    "name": "key2",
                    "paramType": "STRING",
                    "value": "value2"
                },
            ],
            "AsyncStatus": "value1",
            "MessagePayload": "value1"

        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /requests/30397036

    + Body

            {
                 "HandlerAction": {
                          "HandlerStatus": "BIZ_ERROR",
                          "Message": "A Business Error Occured.",
                          "Throwable": {
                              "detailMessage": "The Error",
                              "object" : "value1"
                          }
                 }
            }
